title: Bug 121170 - get column label from metadata object should return some user recognizable strings
description: The bug report is about the getcolumnlabel method not returning user recognizable strings.
OB: The getcolumnlabel should return meaningful labels that can be displayed to the end user.
EB: The getcolumnlabel method should return the same labels before and after extraction.
SR: To reproduce the issue, call the getcolumnlabel method on the metadata object before and after extraction and compare the returned labels.
